948
00:51:30,280 --> 00:51:32,080
 ali njima je to zanimljivo,

949
00:51:32,080 --> 00:51:33,080
 ali opet,

950
00:51:33,080 --> 00:51:33,840
 gubimo,

951
00:51:33,840 --> 00:51:35,480
 gubimo tu čar stvarnosti,

952
00:51:35,480 --> 00:51:36,940
 zapravo dvosjekli mač.

953
00:51:36,940 --> 00:51:39,160
 Eto,

954
00:51:39,160 --> 00:51:44,400
 imaš li onda neki savjet kako naći balans između tog stvarnog svijeta i ovog online svijeta?

955
00:51:44,400 --> 00:51:46,780
 Pa sve ovisi,

956
00:51:46,780 --> 00:51:48,440
 sve ovisi o situaciji,

957
00:51:48,440 --> 00:51:49,560
 kažem,

958
00:51:49,560 --> 00:51:52,200
 neusporedivo i važni stvarni,

959
00:51:52,200 --> 00:51:55,220
 iako i virtualni je na neki način sad postaje stvarni,

960
00:51:55,220 --> 00:51:56,500
 ali opet sad ovisi,

961
00:51:56,500 --> 00:51:58,560
 ima ljudi koji ima su mreže veza,

962
00:51:58,560 --> 00:52:00,200
 neusposa uzeo reču,

963
00:52:00,200 --> 00:52:02,720
