964
00:52:02,720 --> 00:52:04,600
 Sad tu je ono,

965
00:52:04,600 --> 00:52:05,400
 ja sam kad,

966
00:52:05,400 --> 00:52:08,280
 odviđenja nekog videa,

967
00:52:08,280 --> 00:52:09,500
 ono zanimljivog, smiješnog,

968
00:52:09,500 --> 00:52:10,980
 ili to poglaši jedan, drugi, treći,

969
00:52:10,980 --> 00:52:12,000
 odvučete začasti,

970
00:52:12,000 --> 00:52:13,040
 ono, ukrade vrijeme.

971
00:52:13,040 --> 00:52:15,080
 Tako da kažem,

972
00:52:15,080 --> 00:52:17,180
 ono, važna je ta iskrenost prema sebi,

973
00:52:17,180 --> 00:52:18,820
 odgovornost prema svom vremenu,

974
00:52:18,820 --> 00:52:19,580
 prema onome,

975
00:52:19,580 --> 00:52:20,700
 tako da, onako,

976
00:52:20,700 --> 00:52:22,140
 teško je onako,

977
00:52:22,260 --> 00:52:24,600
 ja prvi ne volim kad me neko izdefinira,

978
00:52:24,600 --> 00:52:26,860
 ono, pola sata ću dnevno biti na društvenim vržima,

979
00:52:26,860 --> 00:52:27,640
 ne, ako ne trebam,

980
00:52:27,640 --> 00:52:28,720
