981
00:52:28,720 --> 00:52:31,020
 ali ako imam osjećaj da to ima smisla,

982
00:52:31,020 --> 00:52:33,240
 taj dan ću možda biti dva ili tri sata,

983
00:52:33,240 --> 00:52:33,940
 ono, tako.

984
00:52:33,940 --> 00:52:35,440
 Eto, za kraj,

985
00:52:35,440 --> 00:52:37,040
 imaš li neku univerzalnu poruku

986
00:52:37,040 --> 00:52:37,640
 koju bi, ono,

987
00:52:37,640 --> 00:52:39,380
 poslao mladima koji su zapravo

988
00:52:39,380 --> 00:52:41,180
 tek na početku svog života

989
00:52:41,180 --> 00:52:42,840
 i tek kreću na put?

990
00:52:42,840 --> 00:52:45,280
 Pa, reću da im ništa ne može dati

991
00:52:45,280 --> 00:52:47,540
 veću radost, mir, smisa,

992
00:52:47,660 --> 00:52:48,720
 osim Krista, ono,

993
00:52:48,720 --> 00:52:49,160
 i kažem,

994
00:52:49,160 --> 00:52:49,860
 kogod nas,

995
00:52:49,860 --> 00:52:53,000
 puno stvari nas pokušava prevariti

996
00:52:53,000 --> 00:52:53,780
 ukras nam ga,

997
00:52:53,780 --> 00:52:55,900
 nude nam se neke druge ponude,

998
00:52:55,900 --> 00:52:57,480
 instant rješenja i to je sve,

999
00:52:57,480 --> 00:52:58,660
 ali Krist je jedini

1000
00:52:58,660 --> 00:53:00,680
 koji nam može dati onaj pravi smisao

1001
00:53:00,680 --> 00:53:02,960
 i dovesti nas na onaj cilj koji je nebo,

1002
00:53:02,960 --> 00:53:05,160
 tako da ne isplati se zbog bilo čega

1003
00:53:05,160 --> 00:53:06,740
 na ovom svijetu odustati od njega.

1004
00:53:06,740 --> 00:53:08,500
 Eto, dragi Stjepana,

1005
00:53:08,500 --> 00:53:10,080
 hvala ti što si bio naš gost

1006
00:53:10,080 --> 00:53:11,920
 i što si nas počastio

1007
00:53:11,920 --> 00:53:13,160
 s ovim ugodnim razgovorom.

1008
00:53:13,160 --> 00:53:14,220
 Hvala puno tebi,

1009
00:53:14,220 --> 00:53:15,380
